main event: An unidentified elliptical object was observed descending, hovering briefly, and then departing at a high speed in Wichita, Kansas.
interesting points: The sighting occurred on March 15, 1950 at 6:00 PM., The object was white and about the size of a dinner plate., Witnesses reported the object exhibiting behavior unlike conventional aircraft., The report emphasizes the object's rapid movement after hovering., The memo routing slip mentioned a city with a population of tens of thousands observing the UFO.
witness description: A close observation of the object's behavior by multiple unidentified civilians.
